trans-unit.source: Used in conjunction with signaling the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveProgressChanged"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Brukes sammen med signaliserer i <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveProgressChanged"> </xref> hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: It is signaled whenever a <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecord"></xref> object is found in response to a <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*> operation on a specific <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerName"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Det er signalisert når en <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecord"> </xref> -objekt funnet i svaret på en <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*>operasjon på en bestemt <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerName"> </xref>.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*>

trans-unit.source: If multiple peer name record objects exist in the cloud(s) being queried, this event is signaled once for each record object found.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det finnes flere peer name registrere objekter i cloud(s) som spørres, angis denne hendelsen én gang for hver registrere objektet ble funnet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveCompleted> event is raised only once when all endpoints have been found.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveCompleted>denne hendelsen oppstår når når alle endepunkt er funnet.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveCompleted>

trans-unit.source: Normal process completion implies that either the Resolver object has reached the end of the cloud(s) to query for peer names, or it has reached the maximum number of record entries for the peer name record collection it is constructing.
trans-unit.target: Vanlig prosedyre fullføring antyder at enten Løsningsprogrammet-objektet har nådd slutten av cloud(s) for spørring etter nodenavn, eller den har nådd det maksimale antallet registrere poster for peer name registrere samlingen det er å lage.

trans-unit.source: All references to this instance of the Resolver are coordinated with the token userState <xref:System.Object>, which is a unique identifier for this asynchronous resolve request.
trans-unit.target: Alle referanser til denne forekomsten av av løseren er koordinert med token userState <xref:System.Object>, som er en unik identifikator for denne forespørselen asynkrone Løs.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.ResolveProgressChangedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.ResolveProgressChangedEventArgs"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The resolved peer name is accessible via the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecord.PeerName%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Løst nodenavn er tilgjengelig via den <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecord.PeerName%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecord.PeerName%2A>

trans-unit.source: The user state is inherited from <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs>.
The unique user state object supplied when a <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*> operation was started.
trans-unit.target: Unike tilstand brukerobjektet angitt når en <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*>operasjonen ble startet.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*>
Henter den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecord"> </xref> objekt til å løse.

trans-unit.source: Unsecured peer names can be registered simultaneously by different users in the same <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Cloud>, and associated with different endpoints.
trans-unit.target: Usikker nodenavn kan registreres samtidig av ulike brukere i samme <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Cloud>, og som er forbundet med ulike endepunkt.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Cloud>

trans-unit.source: Consequently, the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver> class is used to resolve peer names to clouds or peer names to peer name records.
trans-unit.target: Derfor kan det <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver>klassen brukes til å løse nodenavn til skyer eller nodenavn peer name-postene.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver>

trans-unit.source: The event to report progress is raised each time a peer name is found while the Resolver is querying clouds for the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerName>.
trans-unit.target: Hendelsen for å rapportere fremdrift oppstår hver gang en nodenavn ble funnet under av løseren spørring skyer for <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerName>.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerName>

trans-unit.source: The peer name record object found in response to a <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*> operation on a specific <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecord.PeerName*>.
trans-unit.target: Peer name post-objekt funnet i svaret på en <> </> *> operasjon på en bestemt <> </> *>.
